ertise in the related field. He is passionate about design, arts, and music...";i:1;s:322:"(Empyrean Design)1992;";}i:55;a:2:{i:0;s:6:"Cancel";i:1;s:6:"Cancel";}i:56;a:2:{i:0;s:84:"* All information will be kept confidential and will not be used by any third party.";i:1;s:65:"* ";}i:57;a:2:{i:0;s:36:"International Students'' Design Forum";i:1;s:24:"";}i:58;a:2:{i:0;s:794:"The objectives of this design forum is to help build students'' confidence in design. <br> We will help them in seeing the physical world in a new realm in order to be more design conscious in problem solving.<br> They will learn through the macro and micro views of components, hence enlarging their perspective in perception in their design concept. </p> <p class=''center''> <strong> - When one cannot see beyond the dimensions of life, nothing profitable can be created. - <br> Eric''s Haywood Chang''s quote </strong> </p> <p> Upon registering with us, students from any design faculty may submit their work for design critics or for discussion.<br> In returned, we will post up these works (after having approval from individual student) for sharing so that more can learn and benefit from it.";i:1;s:708:" <br> </p> <p=''''><strong>- - Eric</strong></p> <p><br>";}i:59;a:2:{i:0;s:36:"International Design Student Contact";i:1;s:24:"";}i:60;a:2:{i:0;s:108:"We would like to know you better, kindly help fill in the as below and all information will be confidential.";i:1;s:81:"";}i:61;a:2:{i:0;s:12:"about_vision";i:1;s:1942:"<p>;</p>\r\n <p class="center">\r\n  <strong> -  - <br> <div style="text-align:right;">() </div>\r\n  </strong>\r\n </p>\r\n <p>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	\r\n </p>\r\n <p class="center">\r\n : <strong></strong>\r\n </p>\r\n <p>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	\r\n </p>";}i:62;a:2:{i:0;s:13:"about_company";i:1;s:2048:"<p>(Empyrean Design)1992;</p>\r\n <p>\r\n  \r\n </p>\r\n <p>\r\n	2004;\r\n </p>\r\n <p>\r\n 2008\r\n </p>\r\n <p>\r\n 2014\r\n </p>";}i:63;a:2:{i:0;s:12:"About Mision";i:1;s:2212